flowchart TD
%% User Authentication Process
    Start([Start]):::info
    EnterCreds[/Enter Credentials/]:::dataLayer
    ValidateFormat{Validate Format}:::warning
    FormatError[\Invalid Format Error\]:::error
    QueryDB[[Query User Database]]:::processingLayer
    UserDB[(User Database)]:::storageLayer
    UserNotFound[\User Not Found Error\]:::error
    VerifyPassword{Verify Password}:::warning
    PasswordError[\Invalid Password Error\]:::error
    GenerateToken[[Generate Session Token]]:::processingLayer
    StoreSession[(Store Session)]:::storageLayer
    Success([Login Success]):::operational
    Start --> EnterCreds
    EnterCreds --> ValidateFormat
    ValidateFormat -->|Invalid| FormatError
    ValidateFormat -->|Valid| QueryDB
    QueryDB --> UserDB
    UserDB -->|Not Found| UserNotFound
    UserDB -->|Found| VerifyPassword
    VerifyPassword -->|No Match| PasswordError
    VerifyPassword -->|Match| GenerateToken
    GenerateToken --> StoreSession
    StoreSession --> Success
